@startuml
title 行情工作流 - 架构图
skinparam shadowing false
skinparam componentStyle rectangle

component "MarketWorkflow" as Workflow
rectangle "BarPipeline" as BarPipeline
rectangle "InstrumentManager" as Instrument
rectangle "PositionAggregate" as Position
rectangle "MarketGateway /\nAccountGateway" as Gateway
rectangle "IndicatorService /\nSignalService" as SignalServices
rectangle "OptionSelector /\nPricing /\nGreeks /\nSizing" as DecisionServices
rectangle "DecisionTrace /\nObservability" as Observability
rectangle "Subscription hooks /\nAutoSave" as RuntimeHooks

Workflow --> BarPipeline : tick 聚合 / bar 转发
Workflow --> Instrument : update_bar / validate_universe
Workflow --> Position : 查持仓 / 关闭仓位
Workflow --> Gateway : 合约、tick、账户数据
Workflow --> SignalServices : 指标计算 / 信号判断
Workflow --> DecisionServices : 选约 / 定价 / Greeks / 仓位
Workflow --> Observability : 发布 trace
Workflow --> RuntimeHooks : 订阅刷新 / autosave / 快照
@enduml
